channel.title: A slight problem?
channel.description:
ok, well i followed [b]ALL[/b] the steps in the tutorial, and it worked right?

i open up no ip, get that running, then start up my server [mind you, it has held over 100 people before] , and when i go to logg into it on silab v4, it wont work.
i tried re-downloading stuff, and still nothing, all i get is an error connecting to server???
wtf? plz help???
